{"tid":1810551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家教協應該仇視教育局","createTime":"2020-01-04T03:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T07:27:35.000Z","uid":115613,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f70ba04f99ae4bedcae8642ca9562a659664631","tid":1810551,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:41:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/教協集會-公然撐教師-有政治立場-214500311.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E7%84%B6%E6%92%90%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB-%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-214500311.html&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=dc371820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/教協集會-公然撐教師-有政治立場-214500311.html</a><br />\n<br />\n集會邀請教育工作者、退休校長及工會代表發言。在去年六月十二日立法會外衝突，被槍傷右眼的教師楊子俊說，右眼視力剩下百分之二點五，屬失明狀態，將向警務處提訴訟。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他指教師必須有政治立場，皆因是《基本法》賦予的政治權利，若如教育局所言，問及政治立場就答不知道，根本未能做好身教的角色</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正面抽擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教育局<br />\n講到做老師都唔洗一般公務員咁政治中立<br />\n睇黎教協已經同政府反哂面<br />\n小二花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49580cfe9ba015379a02f6b5977f30cca88288c","tid":1810551,"uid":292059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"有好過咩？"},{"pid":"fe77620480391476cc098071e7a8d54f8a119c10","tid":1810551,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c49580cfe9ba015379a02f6b5977f30cca88288c","tid":1810551,"uid":292059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"有好過咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"更大矛盾"},{"pid":"f79661a6176d56e06e5fce4579e36dc5b9d52253","tid":1810551,"uid"